message.text:
Honestly, I wasn't supposed to join Creatives or even IABF SC.

As a freshman, I knew that I wanted to join some kind of organization but was unsure what org I should join. I didn't even know what my strengths were but definitely knew that editing was not my strongest suit.

During my summer break before school began, I tried to hone the non-existent skill I had in editing, and when TamHunt 2023 came, I picked Creatives as my 2nd choice and submitted that 1st pubmat as my requirement. All I had was little knowledge in editing, determination, and the willingness to grow. You can imagine how shocked I was when I got accepted !!

In just 2 years in the Student Council, I have can say that I have grown a lot—as a student leader and as a person. In IABF SC, I have found mentors and friends that believed in me and helped me to get out of my comfort zone, to lead with purpose and passion, and carry the skills I have learned with me, always.

OKAY STOP NA ME SA PAGIGING SENTI ✋️😣

BEGINNER OR NOT, this is your sign to join IABF Student Council Creatives Division !! 🫵😼🤍

FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M

message.text:
Honestly, I wasn't supposed to join Creatives or even IABF SC.

As a freshman, I knew that I wanted to join some kind of organization but was unsure what org I should join. I didn't even know what my strengths were but definitely knew that editing was not my strongest suit.

During my summer break before school began, I tried to hone the non-existent skill I had in editing, and when TamHunt 2023 came, I picked Creatives as my 2nd choice and submitted that 1st pubmat as my requirement. All I had was little knowledge in editing, determination, and the willingness to grow. You can imagine how shocked I was when I got accepted !!

In just 2 years in the Student Council, I have can say that I have grown a lot—as a student leader and as a person. In IABF SC, I have found mentors and friends that believed in me and helped me to get out of my comfort zone, to lead with purpose and passion, and carry the skills I have learned with me, always.

message.text:
Honestly, I wasn't supposed to join Creatives or even IABF SC.

As a freshman, I knew that I wanted to join some kind of organization but was unsure what org I should join. I didn't even know what my strengths were but definitely knew that editing was not my strongest suit.

During my summer break before school began, I tried to hone the non-existent skill I had in editing, and when TamHunt 2023 came, I picked Creatives as my 2nd choice and submitted that 1st pubmat as my requirement. All I had was little knowledge in editing, determination, and the willingness to grow. You can imagine how shocked I was when I got accepted !!

In just 2 years in the Student Council, I have can say that I have grown a lot—as a student leader and as a person. In IABF SC, I have found mentors and friends that believed in me and helped me to get out of my comfort zone, to lead with purpose and passion, and carry the skills I have learned with me, always.

OKAY STOP NA ME SA PAGIGING SENTI ✋️😣

BEGINNER OR NOT, this is your sign to join IABF Student Council Creatives Division !! 🫵😼🤍

FEU IABF Student Council S.Y. 2025–2026 divisions: https://bit.ly/IABF_SC_Division_Description_and_Requirements

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
